    "en": {
      "title": "The seats of the two critics of Ranil changed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentarians Tammika Perera, who had criticized President Ranil Wickremesinghe in the past, and Professor G. L. Peiris, who opposed Ranil during the presidential poll, have been replaced in Parliament.",
        "G.L.Pirizi, who was in the front row, has been allotted the second row and Dhammika, who was in the second row, has been allotted seats in the third row."
      ],
